      <h1 class="blog-title">Carbon Monoxide in Liverpool Homes: The Silent Risk Every Homeowner Should Know</h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Carbon monoxide is produced by faulty gas appliances and cannot be seen, smelled or tasted. Here is what every Liverpool homeowner and landlord needs to know to protect their household.</p>
